Text: About half way through descriptive narration kicks in.
Narration SOOO annoying.... Not worth it. I may have to stop my RSS feed from getting from ettv...
They thought the show was so good that halfway through you would go blind by awesomeness.. So they switched to the narrative track

I don't know who's doing that ettv or what, but it's fucking annoying and not clever in any way. It'd be sort of like me handing one of them a copy of the show then punching them in the nose just for effect.
Now I have to go find a non-ettv copy and hope they're not corrupted by fucking retards.
